    "He's lying on the ground, jacket under his head, eyes closed."

    thought "Is he sleeping. On concrete. In December."

    show ist at center_char
    inha "Hey."
    hide ist

    "Nothing."

    show ist at center_char
    inha "Yah. Noh Ye-Jun."
    hide ist

